name: New Orbits
description:
NEW ORBITS - Entry for KENNEY JAM 2021

Help the aliens terraform as many planets as possible, but watch out! Don't crash on their moons or launch yourself in the vast space.

Instructions:

  • SPACE - Jump
  • F - Toggle Fullscreen
  • ESC - Quit

This game also features High Scores. Let's see what you got!
